<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="phone-v">phone <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fəʊn/    美 /foʊn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(给某人) 打电话：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’ll phone you if we have any news. 
如有任何消息，我们会给你打电话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He phoned to invite me out for dinner. 
他打电话请我出去吃饭。</p></div></div>